posts.extended: Joey Lawrence, better known by his professional name, “Joey L.,” is a Canadian commercial photographer, director and published author based in Brooklyn, New York. Visit his website here. PetaPixel: Can you tell us about yourself and how you got started in photography?

On a clear, bright winter day in eastern Mosul’s Al Sukar neighborhood, three black painted pickup trucks zoom along dusty streets, high-pitch sirens whining. Men standing in the vehicles’ open backs wave at nearby drivers to clear a path.
